snippet.title: Gun Raiders - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Gun Raiders is a free-to-play VR shooter for all ages!  Chat with friends while you mow down your enemies in multiple game modes using a broad selection of weapons while flying through the air with your jetpack or climbing monkey-style from wall to wall!  Race to the top of the leaderboards while customizing yourself with all the crazy skins available from the Item Shop.  Updated weekly.  New maps and game modes drop monthly.  Battle Pass coming soon. Join our Discord for tournaments and more!
